data.description: New roof house, new roof shop. 5 year old roof large shop. Pond shallow end stocked with fish. Large oak tress and River Burch trees. Two shops are heated and cooled and wired with lots of 110 and 220 volt receptacles and at 24x24 and 24x40 foot Will accommodate any hobby or man cave or recreation room. House is freshly painted.
data.whatILove: It is close to shopping, restaurants and entertainment in the Snowden Grove neighborhood of stores and amphitheater. two blocks away from North Point Christian school and many churches in the immediate area.
